    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>
                    <bibl><ptr target="#robinson1913"/>, n. <citedRange>49</citedRange>, without illustration</bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#Sammelbuch"/> <citedRange>5897</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>010400</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#belzic2022"/>, catalogue <citedRange>B.69</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64228"><name nymRef="#Θεύχρηστος"><supplied reason="lost">Θ</supplied>εύχρηστος</name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65670"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Σωγένης">Σωγένευς</name></persName></persName>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
           
                
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Theukhrestos fils de Sôgénès.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Theuchrestos son of Sogenes.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Theuchrestos figlio di Sogenes.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>ثيوخريستوس ابن سوجينيس.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>From details given by Robinson (from De Cou's papers), such as a roughly worked back and no mention of a hole on top, it is possible to infer that the base 
                    is rather funerary than dedicatory.</p>
                <p>The date is proposed e.g., from De Cou's normalized copy.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
